text: Novy Subay () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Novosubayevsky Selsoviet, Nurimanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 346 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 24 km from Krasnaya Gorka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Nurimanovsky District
title: Novy Subay
